> assistant
Do you want the script in bash? If so, here it is as a runnable script block:

<RUNNABLE_SCRIPT script-name="count-to-10-with-delay" cwd="." target-shell-type="bash">
``` bash
# count from 1 to 10
for i in {1..10}; do
    # print the current number
    echo "$i"

    # wait for 1 second before the next number
    sleep 1
done
```
</RUNNABLE_SCRIPT>



